for _ in range(int(input())):
 N = int(input())
 ls = list(map(int, input().split()))
 types = []
 type_count = []
 for i in ls:
  if i not in types:
   types.append(i)
 types.sort()
 for j in types:
  indices = []
  for k in range(N):
   if ls[k] == j:
    if k-1 not in indices:
     indices.append(k)
  type_count.append(len(indices))
  
 print(types[type_count.index(max(type_count))])
